    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Theaters devoted primarily to the presentation of such performing art forms as pantomime, puppetry, or shadow shows; popular in France and Italy during the late 19th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
